707169f-a.text: Vanderbilt Avenue, east side, from and including Atlantic Avenue, to, but not including Fulton Street. A view of two 3-story frame houses, along-side of an old public auditorium. In the background, may be seen the steeple of St. Luke's Protestant Episcopal Church. November 26, 1927. P. L. Sperr.
